==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Concert of the powers
<hw>Concert of the powers</hw>. <def>An agreement or understanding
between the chief European powers, the United States, and Japan in 1900
to take only joint action in the Chinese aspect of the Eastern
Question.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Concession</ent>⟦br⟧
